https://lih.kg/2133567</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"cedde3fd80015e739aa9f4f58e7a07b9aa4c0be9","tid":2128400,"uid":46356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d4a7cccbb3fac258c3dbb96db4875db60adbfa38","tid":2128400,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-28T03:09:21.000Z","msg":"鄭月娥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T09:58:49.000Z","msg":"但成日都會被人challenge<br />\n<br />\n&quot;既然林鄭弱智, 咁點解我o地冇人夠佢鬥?&quot;"}]}